        <div class="cs-migration-track">
          <div class="cs-migration-fill"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-migration-date">Legacy fully decommissioned: <span>January 28, 2026</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- AI MULTIPLIER -->
    <section class="cs-section reveal">
      <div class="cs-label">The AI Multiplier</div>
      <h2 class="cs-heading">Design systems are AI infrastructure.</h2>

      <p class="cs-body">When I built the Engineer Self-Serve workflow, the AI needed a design system to work with. Not
        descriptions &mdash; the actual system. Components with real names. Tokens with real values.</p>

      <p class="cs-body"><strong>Techtonic was that system.</strong> 670 components accessible via MCP. When Chothu (our
        AI design consultant) recommends a screen, it uses specific Techtonic components by name.</p>

      <div class="cs-quote">
        <p>The quality of AI-generated design is <strong>directly proportional</strong> to the quality of your design
          system.</p>
      </div>

