    <!-- CRAFT DETAILS -->
    <section class="cs-section reveal">
      <div class="cs-label">Craft</div>
      <h2 class="cs-heading">The details that matter.</h2>

      <h3 class="cs-subheading">The Slab Slam</h3>
      <p class="cs-body">Elements don&rsquo;t fade or bounce &mdash; they <strong>land</strong>. With weight. With
        finality. Haptic feedback synchronized to the animation velocity curve. Motion curves delivered as JSON,
        translated into Flutter animation controllers. Every Techtonic element inherits this vocabulary.</p>

      <div class="cs-visual">
        <div class="cs-visual-inner">Slab slam animation sequence &mdash; 4 frames showing element landing with weight
        </div>
        <div class="cs-visual-caption">Motion with mass. Elements land, they don&rsquo;t bounce.</div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="cs-subheading">Copy as Component</h3>
      <p class="cs-body">The verbal identity encoded into the system &mdash; not as guidelines, but as constraints:</p>

